{"tid":1959592,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［基督徒入］ 我男朋友係耶撚","createTime":"2020-04-05T13:33:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T09:33:39.000Z","uid":255802,"like":4,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"316d9d2254d43c23c88b10479a7aa28fd6d034ca","tid":1959592,"uid":255802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T13:33:28.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n我個男朋友係個好虔誠嘅耶撚<br />\n間教堂佢由細翻到大<br />\n乜嘢將臨期嗰啲都準時翻教會<br />\n佢有時仲話咩預苦期要禁食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原本諗住呢個係佢嘅宗教 <br />\n盡量去respect佢啦<br />\n然後比佢水左幾次去教會玩<br />\n<br />\n但發現間教會唔係好對路<br />\n唔知點解要學啲希伯萊文定唔知乜柒講嘢<br />\n可能見我唔太信蘇哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁佢啲教會弟兄成日比啲說話我聽<br />\n話咩基督徒只可以同返基督徒拍拖架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算而家肺炎<br />\n佢哋都要約出嚟食餐飯然後祈禱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成班人戇鳩鳩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係好想想分手<br />\n對住佢真係頂唔撚順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n忍左佢3年係時候要斬欖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：我平時好respect 唔同宗教<br />\n但係入左魔痴痴地線先會話係耶撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16c0062728ff4f14e61865e405fa807c2d54144","tid":1959592,"uid":173307,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T13:34:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5fae24b6ceb56ea13a2dcef101ca58d350ba307d","tid":1959592,"uid":333095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"316d9d2254d43c23c88b10479a7aa28fd6d034ca","tid":1959592,"uid":255802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":